data.description: Don't miss this beautiful, well maintained 3BR/2BA home in established neighborhood nestled on a quiet street convenient to everything! Hardwood floors throughout, Formal living room, & large sun room with views of private, fenced in backyard. Kitchen appliances include a gas stove top, wall oven with broiler underneath. Beautiful custom built in shelves/entertainment center in living room. HVAC (2021) & Water Heater (2020). Laundry room with plenty of storage located off of carport. Separate, large entertainment house (mother n law suite) (16'X28') complete with covered porch, kitchen, 1/2 Bath, & plenty of storage & room for family & friends to celebrate all of those special occasions. Sprinkler system, large closets, extra front closet & linen closets. Also, extra storage garage for boat, golf cart, ATV, & lawn mower 12'X21 prefab & lean-to. Over 2000 square feet of living & entertainment space.
